&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description - Country Head - Vietnam&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Anchanto, we know that the one of the keys to growth is a high-performing team. That’s why we’re seeking a skilled Country Head for the Vietnam. The ideal candidate will have experience in B2B SaaS ecommerce product sales management, as well as skills related to strategic analysis and marketing. In this role, you will handle the P&amp;amp;L of the country with a full responsibility of the revenue and the expenses for the operations. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; As a Country Head for Anchanto’s products focused on Enterprise segment, you will have the opportunity to help promote growth and shape the future of SaaS products for eCommerce players in the Retail and Logistics sector. We will rely on you to partner with our sales and marketing department to conduct market research and develop a strategic business development plan. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Reporting directly to the Chief Revenue Officer APAC, your key goal will be to drive substantial revenue growth - through New-Logo Sell, Upsell and Cross-Sell - by deepening consultative relationship. You will play a crucial role in finding and executing cross-selling and upselling opportunities, ensuring that our solutions not only address current client needs but also expect future challenges, fostering long-term partnerships and sustainable growth.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a quota holding role, there will be an annual target, and an incentive plan linked.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#1 Sales &amp;amp; Revenue Leadership and Business Expansion  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Logos:&lt;/strong&gt; Responsible for achieving year-over-year topline growth in the Vietnam by meeting sales targets for both personal and team performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Existing Revenue:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure 100% renewal of all current customers, with a focus on potential growth and backlog revenue expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Growth Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive growth primarily through new customer acquisitions, supplemented by upselling and cross-selling to existing clients. Set and achieve quarterly sales targets for both yourself and your team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and manage a strong customer pipeline in the Vietnam, directly engaging in high-value deals and CXO-level relationships.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#2 P&amp;amp;L Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
