&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Budget Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the country’s budget, including headcount, outsourced services, office leases, and marketing expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROI Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure sustainable, long-term ROI to maintain a positive P&amp;amp;L in the Vietnam.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual Planning:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and agree on annual plans and timelines with Executive Management and internal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
