&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development&lt;/strong&gt;: Market research, pipeline development, and collaboration with internal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Development&lt;/strong&gt;: Staying updated on industry trends and building brand presence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate should have a proven record in software sales, experience in industries like FMCG or logistics, and the ability to manage complex SaaS deal cycles.&lt;/p&gt;
