&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate records of prospecting activities, pipeline development, and sales metrics in the CRM system to ensure visibility and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback to marketing and BDR teams on inbound leads to be serviced.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
