&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in consultative conversations with prospects to understand their business needs and how Anchanto can help their business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tailor sales presentations to address the unique needs of prospects, demonstrating how Anchanto’s platform solves key business challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
