&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Workforce Planning: Partner with leaders on headcount planning, capability assessments, skills forecasting, and workforce strategies aligned to business growth plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
