&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;How You Will Build at&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;Anchanto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245418&amp;qu

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Marketing Manager to join our marketing team and lead marketing initiatives across&amp;nbsp;Malaysia and Singapore markets. Based in Malaysia, you will work closely with our APAC Marketing Director to&amp;nbsp;manage comprehensive go-to-market strategies across digital channels, events, and account-based marketing&amp;nbsp;programs to drive qualified pipeline for our enterprise solutions. This role requires both strategic thinking and&amp;nbsp;hands-on execution, along with cross-functional collaboration with Central Marketing and Regional Sales teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute integrated marketing channel strategies across Malaysia and Singapore markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage full-funnel demand generation programs from awareness through conversion, optimizing&amp;nbsp;campaigns to generate high-quality leads across both markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt and implement country-specific and segment-specific key messaging in campaigns and marketing&amp;nbsp;assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and execute events to create engagement opportunities with target accounts and drive pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Sales teams on pipeline targets, report on pipeline performance, and implement ABM&amp;nbsp;plays for target accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and analyze campaign performance, pipeline metrics, and conversion rates, and provide regular&amp;nbsp;reports to stakeholders on market performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, maintain, and optimize campaign landing pages, nurture sequences, and retargeting flows that&amp;nbsp;convert awareness into qualified opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Central Marketing Team for design, content production, local website updates, event&amp;nbsp;branding, and campaign assets while maintaining brand consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source and coordinate with local vendors for creative production and merchandising needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare, update, and maintain marketing reports and documentation on schedule and adhere to process&amp;nbsp;workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of marketing experience, preferably in B2B marketing or SaaS environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience executing multi-channel campaigns and events in Malaysia and/or Singapore with an&amp;nbsp;understanding of local business culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of measurable results in lead generation and pipeline contribution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in English with excellent writing and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in e-commerce, supply chain, logistics, or omnichannel commerce technology sectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in ABM and enterprise marketing targeting mid-market to enterprise accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with HubSpot, Salesforce, or similar marketing automation and CRM platforms.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
