&lt;h2 class=&quot;fb921db8 _0c74bc36 _7e82b501 bbf7948c _98c4b229 eba9bbe3 a8ea6bf6 _7b625940 _3a0901f3 _586c9f71 _29670e17&quot;&gt;About the job&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;fb921db8 f6f3d167 bbf7948c _98c4b229 ca60e040 f46b3150 _7b625940 _3a0901f3 _586c9f71 _29670e17 ede8882d&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_359e3235 _93797b7c _2dce6504&quot; data-testid=&quot;expandable-text-box&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Anchanto&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Anchanto is a Global B2B SaaS product company headquartered in Singapore with operations across 14+ countries. Through its award-winning SaaS products and solutions, Anchanto enables eCommerce Brands, Retailers, Online Sellers, SMEs, 3PLs, eCommerce enablers/Distributors manage &amp;amp; run highly successful end-to-end eCommerce operations across Asia Pacific.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;With the philosophy of making ‘multichannel selling and eCommerce logistics’ simple for everyone, Anchanto was founded by Mr. Vaibhav Dabhade in June 2011. Today, 7200+ businesses run highly successful eCommerce operations through the Anchanto platform. Our customer base comprises global players such as L&#39;Oréal, Luxasia, DKSH Asia, Asendia, Pos Malaysia, DHL eCommerce, MYDIN, Jay Gee, Telkom Indonesia, and many more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Anchanto operates from its offices and teams across Singapore, India, Malaysia, Indonesia, Philippines and Australia. We continue to grow multi-fold month-on-month, with our growing customer base managing 58+ million SKUs &amp;amp; 102+ million product listings, and processing 31+ million orders worth a Gross Merchandise Value (GMV) of 1.27+ Billion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Designer (3–5 Years Experience) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview :&lt;/strong&gt; As a Product Designer at Anchanto, you will help shape the user experience across our suite of Enterprise SaaS products, including Order Management (OMS), Warehouse Management (WMS), and Omnichannel Commerce solutions. You will work closely with Product Managers, Engineers, and Senior Designers to transform complex operational workflows into intuitive, scalable, and customer-centric experiences. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys solving real-world business problems, designing for data-rich environments, and contributing to a growing design system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Role Exists &lt;/strong&gt;Anchanto is continuously expanding its product ecosystem to support global retailers, brands, distributors, and logistics providers. As our platform grows, we need designers who can:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve usability across our products.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simplify operational workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistency through our Design System.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accelerate product delivery through scalable design practices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI-powered tools to improve design efficiency and innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities / What You Will Own&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Design user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Translate business requirements into intuitive user experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Simplify complex workflows related to inventory, logistics, warehouse operations, and order fulfillment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Create responsive and accessible experiences across web applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;stron

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MailCompose&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As an Product Manager for Connected solutions – You will own the strategy, roadmap, and execution for Anchanto’s integration ecosystem across carriers, marketplaces, ERP systems, SAP, webstore aggregators, plugins, and omni-channel store app capabilities, WMS, OMS. The role will work closely with Engineering, QA, Delivery, Customer Success, Support, and external partners to translate business and customer needs into scalable product capabilities.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The role requires a strong understanding of OMS, WMS, e-commerce order processing, API-driven product development, and integration design. The person should be able to manage senior internal stakeholders and external customers, lead a team of 2 APMs, make structured product decisions, and articulate requirements clearly and crisply.&lt;/div&gt;
