&lt;li&gt;Build a scalable product approach for reusable plugins, connectors, and partner onboarding models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate customer demand, market opportunities, implementation pain points, and product gaps to shape roadmap priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance short-term business opportunities with long-term platform scalability and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
