&lt;li&gt;Review team work outputs and ensure consistency, completeness, and clarity in requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define functional and non-functional requirements for integration features, including performance, reliability, security, configurability, monitoring, and scale.&lt;/li&gt;
