&lt;li&gt;Allocate work effectively across roadmap, BAU, issue resolution, and strategic initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build ownership, accountability, and strong execution discipline within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive NFRs and integration compliance related activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
