&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and track success metrics for integration initiatives such as delivery timelines, adoption, onboarding speed, defect trends, implementation effort, support escalations, and customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure plugin and connector reusability to reduce repeated custom development effort.&lt;/li&gt;
