&lt;li&gt;Evaluate opportunities for ecosystem integrations and operational enhancements that strengthen the OMS value proposition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build product direction around modern retail use cases such as ship-from-store, click-and-collect, multi-node fulfillment, order modification, and cross-channel customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
