&lt;h3 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;171&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;126&quot; data-end=&quot;140&quot;&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; Program Manager – CEO Office&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;178&quot; data-end=&quot;203&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;182&quot; data-end=&quot;201&quot;&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;204&quot; data-end=&quot;601&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly independent, organized, and strategic &lt;strong data-start=&quot;266&quot; data-end=&quot;298&quot;&gt;Program Manager – CEO Office&lt;/strong&gt; to work closely with the CEO and drive high-impact business initiatives while owning cross-functional projects. This role requires a proactive and detail-oriented professional who can manage complex projects, collaborate with senior leadership, and ensure alignment with the company’s vision and goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;603&quot; data-end=&quot;807&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will have an execution-first attitude, strong planning and organizing skills, excellent communication ability, and the ability to thrive in a fast-paced, technology-driven environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;814&quot; data-end=&quot;845&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;818&quot; data-end=&quot;843&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;847&quot; data-end=&quot;896&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;852&quot; data-end=&quot;896&quot;&gt;Program Management &amp;amp; Strategic Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;897&quot; data-end=&quot;1440&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;897&quot; data-end=&quot;1023&quot;&gt;
