&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role exists to manage the Sales Development/Lead Generation operations in Thailand.&amp;nbsp; The role has ownership of generating and converting pipeline of customer for Anchanto’s products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bangkok, Thailand&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can be Working out of Home / Office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sales Development Representative, Thailand&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Sales Development Representative for Anchanto’s products (OMS and WMS) focused on Enterprise segment, you will have the exciting opportunity to help promote the growth and shape the future of SaaS products for eCommerce players in the Retail and Logistics sector.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will possess both business development and technical background that enables them to engage at with C-level executives as well as with software developers and IT architects. They should also be a self-starter, prepared to develop and execute to increase market penetration across Thailand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Impact market share in the Thailand territory or industry vertical.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct sales development for software sales to enterprises (Brand Principals, Distributors, 3PLs, Warehousing Companies, E-distributors, Retailers) to build strong B2B SaaS business in Thailand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Lead generation&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a funnel pipeline: Manage entire sales cycle (as individual contributor) steps such as cold call, LinkedIn emails, personal networking etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand Customers&#39; current Business and Operational processes to propose the right fit of SaaS products, Understanding the customer pain points, Map to Solutioning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Demoing the Product/Solution &lt;/em&gt;: Product introduction SaaS platform demonstration, explanation of technical and functional capabilities, Understand and consult on a strategic and business level, available integrations and flows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Assist with Contract Closure&lt;/em&gt;: follow-up call, sharing updates and assisting with proposal, pricing negotiation, contract signing, on-boarding and account handover to global account management teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured and organised to manage and update the CRM tool for effective Sales Pipeline management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business and Commercial Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess the technical ability to explain (not implement) Cloud/SaaS Solutions, Integrations, Retail, Omni-channel and eCommerce Fulfilment flows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create &amp;amp; articulate compelling value propositions around Retail Solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of Value Based Selling and translate it into Commercial Agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the internal marketing team, PR team and top management to swiftly pickup lead/enquires / suspects to be put in sales processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
